This document is a list of 132 candidates for the computer engineering program ranked by their merit scores. Candidates must confirm their acceptance between September 1-5, 2016 by submitting a copy of their baccalaureate diploma, or they will be eliminated from the list. The list provides each candidate's code, name, date of birth, calculated average, and ranking.
